# AV Messenger

AV Messenger is an Android chat application built with Java and Firebase. The app provides user authentication, profile creation, a contact/user list, real-time one-to-one messaging, and basic profile settings.

## Overview

This project is a simple messaging app that allows users to:

- create an account and sign in
- set a profile image and status
- browse other registered users
- open private chat conversations
- send and receive messages in real time
- log out securely

## Features

- Firebase Authentication for email/password sign-in and registration
- Firebase Realtime Database for storing user data and chat messages
- Firebase Storage for profile image uploads
- Splash screen and login/registration flow
- User list screen with profile details
- Chat screen with message sending and receiving
- Profile settings screen for updating display name and status
- Material Design UI with RecyclerView for lists

## Tech Stack

- Android Studio
- Java
- AndroidX / Material Components
- Firebase Authentication
- Firebase Realtime Database
- Firebase Storage
- Picasso for image loading
- CircleImageView for circular profile photos

